@startuml
[*] --> WaitingForInput : Start
WaitingForInput --> SelectPredefinedAmount : Choose predefined amount
SelectPredefinedAmount --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Process withdrawal
ProcessingWithdrawal --> WithdrawalCompleted : Withdrawal successful
ProcessingWithdrawal --> CancelTransaction : User cancels transaction
CancelTransaction --> StopTransaction : Stop transaction and return card

[*] --> CustomAmountEntry : Enter custom amount
CustomAmountEntry --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Process withdrawal
ProcessingWithdrawal --> WithdrawalCompleted : Withdrawal successful
ProcessingWithdrawal --> CancelTransaction : User cancels transaction
CancelTransaction --> StopTransaction : Stop transaction and return card

[*] --> TransactionCancelled : User cancels transaction
TransactionCancelled --> StopTransaction : Stop transaction and return card

StopTransaction --> [*] : End
@enduml
